headline: Pro-Trump senator meets China's economy tsar amid trade tensions
summary: U.S. Senator Steve Daines,a strong supporter of President Donald Trump, met with China’seconomy tsar, Vice Premier He Lifeng, on Saturday, marking thefirst visit by a U.S. politician to Beijing...
